data.description: Discover your home! This charming 3-bedroom, 1and a half bath gem offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and timeless character. With a spacious layout, gleaming hardwood style floors, and a large backyard. The garage is deep enough to possibly fit four cars. Or use a portion as storage or work room.  Located in the near the Bishop Arts District, you'll enjoy easy access to amenities and a vibrant community. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your forever home. Call today and start living the Dallas dream!
